<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>水晶 on Lucky Stone</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</link><description>Recent content in 水晶 on Lucky Stone</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>紫水晶 x 眉心輪 &amp; 頂輪：一顆石頭，同時打開兩個靈性能量中心</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E8%84%88%E8%BC%AA%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E7%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E8%BC%AA%E8%88%87%E9%A0%82%E8%BC%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;大多數水晶只對應一個脈輪。紫水晶不一樣——它同時連結眉心輪和頂輪，也就是七脈輪體系裡最頂端的兩個能量中心。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶功效完整解析：靈性修行入門首選</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E5%8A%9F%E6%95%88%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9D%88%E6%80%A7%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%A5%E9%96%80%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;在水晶店走了一圈，最後手裡還是捧著一顆紫水晶——你不孤單，幾乎每個人的起點都在這裡。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶怎麼用？冥想、助眠、空間淨化實戰完整指南</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8%E5%86%A5%E6%83%B3%E5%8A%A9%E7%9C%A0%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8%E5%86%A5%E6%83%B3%E5%8A%A9%E7%9C%A0%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E5%AF%A6%E6%88%B0%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;買了紫水晶，然後呢？&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶星座配對：雙魚、水瓶、射手為什麼特別有緣？</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;同樣一顆紫水晶，有人戴了感覺渾身舒暢，有人帶了幾個月幾乎沒感覺。這不全然是「信不信的問題」——星座跟水晶的共振確實有差。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶淨化方法完整指南：月光浴、煙燻、聲音療癒怎麼選？</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E6%9C%88%E5%85%89%E6%B5%B4%E7%85%99%E7%87%BB%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3%E7%99%82%E7%99%92%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E9%81%B8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E6%9C%88%E5%85%89%E6%B5%B4%E7%85%99%E7%87%BB%E8%81%B2%E9%9F%B3%E7%99%82%E7%99%92%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E9%81%B8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;水晶需要淨化——這件事很多人知道，但真正做到的不多。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>